    "title": "Process Engineer Vacancy at JSW Steel Global Group - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Process Engineer with drive and ambition, JSW Steel Global Group in Jaipur is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout JSW Steel Global Group:\nJSW Steel Global Group is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with JSW Steel Global Group!",
